title: Building An Empire With Hair Extraordinaire Becky Miller
description: Becky Miller is "goals" when it comes to building a hair empire. This salon owner, product creator, and master educator has been in the industry for 15 years and has built quite a name for herself! We're talking babies, business, and the path she's walked that has brought her to where she is today launching her own line of foils, Modern Foil, and the massive love the hair community has shown her new venture!
